data.description: This home is located on a large, mature treed lot in sought after area. With laminate flooring and tile throughout, lots of natural lighting, a large fireplace in the family room, and exemplary Conroe ISD schools, this one won't last long. Located near parks, shopping, dining and convenient to highways for commutes, this cul de sac  lot is ready for your backyard oasis designs. Schedule your appointment today so you don't miss out on this great deal.
